<font color="#ffffff">I promise.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

348
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:48,320
<font color="#ffffff">Good luck!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

349
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:50,720
<font color="#ffffff">I'll be waiting to hear</font><font color="#ffffff">
