446
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:26,760
<font color="#ffffff">You're really something, Sai Kaew.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

447
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:31,000
<font color="#ffffff">How could Petch look past you?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

448
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:32,640
<font color="#ffffff">Shut up!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

449
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:37,640
<font color="#ffffff">I know you're hurting.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

