00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,320
<font color="#ffffff">I am too.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

451
00:37:49,600 --> 00:37:52,480
<font color="#ffffff">I have no one left.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

