512
00:45:06,520 --> 00:45:08,120
<font color="#ffffff">But it feels nice.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

513
00:45:11,600 --> 00:45:13,000
<font color="#ffffff">Laughing together like this…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

514
00:45:14,840 --> 00:45:17,120
<font color="#ffffff">makes me feel like a kid again.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

515
